title: The Treehouse Coffee Shop
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegan choices include all lunch sandwiches (substitute vegan chicken patty), some salads, seasonal soups like pumpkin, oatmeal, desserts like pumpkin bread, muffins and cookies. Has gluten free choices. Organic and fair trade coffee available. Provides party and holiday catering.
